                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180506-118-off671 t18180506-118-crimeloc674"></join>. On the 14th of April, about twelve o'clock, I put my coat over a chair in the hall, and went into the drawing-room to my mistress-the housekeeper called me - I found the prisoner in custody, and the coat lying on the floor.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180506-118-person1003">
                  MARGARET 
