            . I am housekeeper to Lady 
               <persName id="t18180506-118-person1004">
                  Mary 
                  Wake
               <interp inst="t18180506-118-person1004" type="surname" value="Wake"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180506-118-person1004" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180506-118-person1004" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming out of the kitchen about twelve o'clock, and saw the prisoner come out of the servant's hall - He asked if Jones lived there? I told him No - He came down the area; I saw the coat lying at his feet. I took hold of him, thinking he might have some plate, and called Hilson. The prisoner pulled me up several of the area steps, trying to get away - I still held him. A crowd gathered round. He returned to the hall, and the butler and footman secured him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was sent to Mr. Jones's to beat carpets. I made no resistance.</p>
               <p>
